 the air with his car key, on her left, on her right. Theaquamarine sky was now silent, darkish and empty, save for a star-shapedstar about which I wrote a Russian elegy ages ago, in another world.

"What a charming, good-natured, civilized, sexy young fellow," saidLouise as we stamped into the lift. "Are you in the mood tonight? Rightaway, Vad?" <196>





